Package model

package model
Contains various data classes for storing game data and media resources
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    ButtonDisplayModel
    Class that tries to read custom images, linking images to set names in a hashmap making it easier to use them later.
    GameTracker
    Class that keeps track of the current game of blackjack.
    ImageDisplayModel
    Class that tries to read custom images for all the playing cards, linking images to set names in a hashmap making it easier to use them later.
    SoundEffectModel
    Class that tries to play sound files.
